<p>星联英语补习班：Moonlight</p>

<ul>
  <li>Noun.
    <ul>
      <li>the light of the moon.</li>
      <li>月光</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Verb (used without object), moon·light·ed, moon·light·ing.
    <ul>
      <li>to work at a secondary job, esp at night, and often illegitimately.</li>
      <li>暗地里（晚上月光下）偷鸡摸狗做某事</li>
      <li>例句：He had been moonlighting for a rival tabloid.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

